WEBVTT

00:00:27.280 --> 00:00:31.256
biroq o'sha daqiqada uning harakatlari

00:00:31.280 --> 00:00:32.920
mazmunini anglash istagi uyg’ondi,

00:00:33.760 --> 00:00:36.536
hayotim bilan qarzdor bo’lgan,
o’z hayotini xatarga

00:00:36.560 --> 00:00:38.416
qo’yib o'zga kishining hayotin qutqardi

00:00:38.440 --> 00:00:42.056
undagi qanday ichki kuch bu tanlovni

00:00:42.080 --> 00:00:47.120
berdi. Boshqacha aytganda,
u yoki har kimning altruistik xulqni

00:00:47.840 --> 00:00:49.856
namoyon etishiga nima
turtki bo’ladi? Ammo

00:00:49.880 --> 00:00:51.336
undan oldin nima bo'lganini

00:00:51.360 --> 00:00:53.736
aytib berishga ijozat bering. 
19 yoshda edim,

00:00:53.760 --> 00:00:55.576
Takomadagi uyimizga mashinada

00:00:55.600 --> 00:00:58.136
qaytayotgan edim.
To’satdan mashinam qarshisidan

00:00:58.160 --> 00:01:00.496
kuchukcha chiqib qoldi va men
qilmasligimiz kerak